Note on dependencies:

Chronicler depends on YantrikDB (https://github.com/yantrikos/yantrikdb),
which is licensed under AGPL-3.0. Using YantrikDB as-is via its MCP server
(the default in Chronicler's docker-compose) does not trigger AGPL
obligations on your code. Modifying the YantrikDB engine and distributing it
or providing it as a network service does trigger AGPL.
